     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复为可更新视图执行查询重写后可能的崩溃
      (Stephen Frost)
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
     <para>
      Fix planner's handling of <literal>LATERAL</> references (Tom
